author: Linus Tech Tips
description:
#ad 

Welcome to ROG Rig Reboot 2025! 

We're excited to announce that we've once again partnered with our friends at ASUS to give our viewers the opportunity to be in flown to Linus Media Group HQ,  where they'll build a PC with Linus for a video!

The name of the game is simple. Submit a video showing us why you need a Rig Reboot. Whether your system is unable to keep up with your workflow, can't run demanding games, or is just absolutely cooked, we need the details. 

This is a competition that rewards creativity and originality, so make sure your video is unique and not reminiscent of previous submissions. Yes, we'll know. 

Video Requirements

30-60 Seconds
Show us your current setup
Tell us why we should pick YOU! 
#ROGRigReboot25 in the video description
and again, be creative! 

*If you miss any of these requirements, your entry will be disqualified*

*Entries will be accepted until this form closes on May 25th, 11:45PM (GMT)*
title: fine, ill give away a free pc - ASUS ROG RIG REBOOT ANNOUNCMENT
